ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 6 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Highlights of Stage 6, Epernay to Metz.
